<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><!DOCTYPE paragraph PUBLIC "-//IFRS//DTD DITA Paragraph//EN" "../../../DocTypes/com.ifrs.doctype/dtd/paragraph.dtd"><paragraph id="IAS19_140" base="F16152230" principles="no"><paranum class="- topic/title paragraph/paranum "/><titlealts><navtitle>140</navtitle></titlealts><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IAS&#xa0;19"/><data name="paranum" value="140"/></prolog><body><p id="IAS19_P0625">An entity shall provide a reconciliation from the opening balance to the closing balance for each of the following, if applicable:</p><ol outputclass="static" id="IAS19_L0078" base="F16152232" type="lower-alpha"><li id="IAS19_140_a"><li_value>(a)</li_value> <p id="IAS19_P0626" base="F16152233">the net defined benefit liability (asset), showing separate reconciliations for:</p> <ol outputclass="static" id="IAS19_L0079" base="F16152678" type="lower-roman"><li id="IAS19_140_a_i"><li_value>(i)</li_value> <p id="IAS19_P0627" base="F16152679">plan assets.</p></li><li id="IAS19_140_a_ii"><li_value>(ii)</li_value> <p id="IAS19_P0628" base="F16152681">the present value of the defined benefit obligation.</p></li><li id="IAS19_140_a_iii"><li_value>(iii)</li_value> <p id="IAS19_P0629" base="F16152683">the effect of the asset ceiling.</p></li></ol></li><li id="IAS19_140_b"><li_value>(b)</li_value> <p id="IAS19_P0630" base="F16152685">any reimbursement rights. An entity shall also describe the relationship between any reimbursement right and the related obligation.</p></li></ol></body></paragraph>